      <h2>Start Coding</h2>
      <i class="fa fa-code"></i>
        <p>The program starts with 2 years of weekly classes to supplement school learning in Java.</p>
        <p>If you don’t have this baseline you may need to complete a bridging course to get up to speed.</p>
        <p><strong>The most important things are a passion for tech and a drive to learn.</strong></p>
      <h2>Solidify Learning</h2>
      <i class="fa fa-graduation-cap"></i>
        <p>After passing your tests, you’ll move into CapaCiti for a 6-month course to solidify your learning in Java and JavaScript.</p>
        <p>Thanks to Oracle and the Western Cape Government, the course is free to students.</p>
